Package: easyPlots
Title: Tools for Plotting and GO Enrichment Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alvaro", "Gutierrez", email = "gutierrez.alvaro.o.c@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of tools to create customizable plots and perform Gene Ontology 
    enrichment analysis using clusterProfiler and other packages. Includes functions 
    to generate volcano plots, ontology plots, and GO enrichment summaries with optional 
    translation and filtering capabilities.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
